# AgentQMS Rules

## SST Reference
- MUST read `AgentQMS/knowledge/agent/system.md` (SST) before acting
- Reference SST for details; don't repeat comprehensive guidance here

## Automation
- Use automation only: `cd AgentQMS/interface && make help` for commands
- NEVER create artifacts manually; use `make create-*` targets
- Always validate after changes: `make validate && make compliance`

## Artifacts
- Naming format: `YYYY-MM-DD_HHMM_[type]_name.md`
- Location: `docs/artifacts/` subdirectories by type
- Frontmatter date: `YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM (KST)` format required

## Context Discovery
- Use `make context` (auto-detects) or `make context-[domain]`
- Architecture files: `.agentqms/state/architecture.yaml`, `.copilot/context/tool-catalog.md`, `.copilot/context/workflow-triggers.yaml`

## Path Management
- Use `PYTHONPATH=.` from project root for AgentQMS tools
- NEVER manually manipulate `sys.path`

## Artifact Creation Commands
- ✅ `make create-plan NAME=name TITLE="Title"`
- ✅ `make create-assessment NAME=name TITLE="Title"`
- ✅ `make create-bug-report NAME=name TITLE="Title"`
- ❌ NEVER create artifacts manually in `docs/artifacts/`
